Minimalistic style: A single, elegant mind map drawn in clean black ink lines radiating organically from a central node, floating against a soft cream background. The branches curl and split like tree limbs or neural pathways, with small colorful nodes at each endpoint rendered as simple geometric shapes in muted primary colors. One branch visibly wilts and fades to gray, its nodes becoming hollow circles. A small window in the corner shows bright sunshine and green grass outside, casting a warm golden rectangle of light across the composition. The overall feeling is one of structured potential meeting gentle disappointment.
